# Netlify/Vercel SPA Redirects
# Handle client-side routing for Single Page Application

# API routes - proxy to backend
/api/*  /api/:splat  200

# Handle all other routes as SPA
/*    /index.html   200

# Redirect non-www to www
https://debtsystemmanager.com/*  https://www.debtsystemmanager.com/:splat  301
http://debtsystemmanager.com/*  https://www.debtsystemmanager.com/:splat  301

# Force HTTPS
http://www.debtsystemmanager.com/*  https://www.debtsystemmanager.com/:splat  301
